nodes.text: Didyma V was a terrestrial world that was the homeworld of the Didynon Engi Golba. Lommite, a type of ore used in transparisteel, was mined on the world.

By 35 ABY, the First Order, the successor state of the Galactic Empire, had annexed Didyma V, taking control of the lommite production. Golba escaped from the mines after its annexation to join the Resistance, a paramilitary group led by former New Republic senator Leia Organa.
Didyma V was first mentioned in the 2019 reference book Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker: The Visual Dictionary, written by Pablo Hidalgo.
